P framework designed for building modern web applications quickly and efficiently', '2025-12-17 17:04:05.102063+00'), (8, 'MySQL', 'https://qxlpgsghajxthihcpqwr.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/portfolio-images/tech-0.5199078349408015.png', 'database', 100, 1, 'MySQL is an open-source relational database management system (RDBMS) that uses Structured Query Language (SQL) to store, manage, and retrieve data.', '2025-12-17 17:05:23.296948+00'), (9, 'PostgreSQL', 'https://qxlpgsghajxthihcpqwr.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/portfolio-images/tech-0.8401635517439732.svg', 'database', 90, 1, 'PostgreSQL is a powerful, open-source object-relational database management system (ORDBMS) known for its reliability, extensibility, and standards compliance', '2025-12-17 17:30:53.800248+00');